## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and expert opinions, which may not encompass all perspectives or recent developments in the field of higher education. Additionally, the societal and individual benefits of higher education can vary significantly across different regions and demographic groups, which may not be fully captured in this report. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.